    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This car is in stunning, showroom-ready condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a charm, and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy the ride. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in top-notch shape, you've found it! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
