    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For the purist seeking an unadulterated analog experience, this 1997 Acura NSX-T is presented in concours-level condition. Powered by the C32B 3.2L VTEC V6 paired with a close-ratio 6-speed manual gearbox, it features the factory-upgraded helical limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The all-aluminum monocoque and double-wishbone suspension components are free of oxidation, maintaining the structural integrity and 42/58 weight distribution that defined this mid-engine icon. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a fresh timing belt/water pump kit. This is a turnkey, investment-grade example with zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 44900.0,
